+**Architecture:** The engine has 4 layers: (1) cell reference parsing, (2) formula tokenizer/parser producing an AST, (3) formula evaluator that walks the AST, (4) dependency graph for reactive updates. The `Spreadsheet` class ties them together, storing raw values and recomputing dependents on change.
